{"tid":1763053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]開闢新戰線，支爆個頭近！","createTime":"2019-11-30T04:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T05:28:35.000Z","uid":304937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"618841ff66b039563b6deb582d976315d9abf729","tid":1763053,"uid":304937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:39:38.000Z","msg":"1. 由南至北既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">革命輸出</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n南方人民素來離心力強，何不「絕其智而用其力」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />農民絕對係最精銳既革命部隊，個個視死如歸，又牛高馬大。自清朝鴉片戰爭以來，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>廣州</strong></span></span>國民先係堅拒洋人入城，後又有《東南互保章程》，根本就完全唔聽中央講。廣州人素來有風骨，今次反對起火葬場就知道咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再講日日高呼「福建獨立」既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><em><span style=\"color: red;\">福建</span></em></em></strong></span>，你估真係無獨立過啊？民國先挽過好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由南邊作為反共基地絕對唸得過，何樂而不為呢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.輸出<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">方法</span></span></strong><br />\n改變玻璃國人民撚法相當簡單，佢地大多人云亦云，無個人批判思考可言。所以，力推今次廣州國國民反對火葬場成功既例子，完全可以作為「民主是個好東西」既基礎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多啲係微博、微信朋友圈、QQ等等內地apps洗版，令到多啲五毛跟風，自然就開始質疑支共統治既合法性，質疑支共本身制度問題，質疑雜種既統治地位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果，各省獨立，支爆近了。<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>外國勢力</strong></span></span>介入？<br />\n可能到時，中華人民玻璃國又會好似清朝咁，名存實亡。被人瓜分，各取其利。中華人民玻璃國只空有其名，而無統治權。或許，國民又會覺醒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論係點，玻璃國點都會碎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好好發展國內戰線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw，記得send呢幾張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSQkJnO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSQkJnO.jpg&h=510cc1bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMemsPv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMemsPv.png&h=ee8d923d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcab8b4230ecbfd5ab6175b9b264928871fb4d2d","tid":1763053,"uid":304937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab091d2a4f46ba6f25172e3ea0ab8ecd8be1a049","tid":1763053,"uid":304937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324254b121c58aced078c1b07e230d